        <Parent_String>Mucoromycotina (class) [300378942], Zygomycota (phylum) [300378943], Fungi (kingdom) [300265679], Eukaryota (domain) [300265677], living organisms (entities) [300390503], Living Organisms (hierarchy name) [300265673], Agents Facet [300264089]</Parent_String>
